    • Uses of IdGeneratorFactory in org.neo4j.internal.id

      Classes in org.neo4j.internal.id that implement IdGeneratorFactory 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  BufferingIdGeneratorFactory
      Wraps IdGenerator so that ids can be freed using reuse marker at safe points in time, after all transactions which were active at the time of freeing, have been closed.
      class  DefaultIdGeneratorFactory  
      class  ScanOnOpenOverwritingIdGeneratorFactory
      A DefaultIdGeneratorFactory that ignores any existing id file on open and instead replaces it with an id file of the current format with the highId it got from scanning the store on open.
      class  ScanOnOpenReadOnlyIdGeneratorFactory
      IdGeneratorFactory that ignores the underlying id file and only uses the provided highIdScanner in open(PageCache, Path, IdType, LongSupplier, long, boolean, PageCursorTracer, ImmutableSet), instantiating IdGenerator that will return that highId and do nothing else.
